summary: As the name suggests, Kountervibe ENB Supplemental is designed as supplement Kyo's beautiful Kountervibe ENB Northern Light preset. It adds my personal tweaks to a few of the unique weathers found in Skyrim that weren't technically covered in Kyo's Northern Light preset. More weather types may be added in future.
